As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 398 people, 149 households, and 107 families residing in the CDP.<ref>{{Cite web|title=HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES:2020|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Acacia+Villas+CDP;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|access-date=2023-07-17|website=data.census.gov}}</ref>

===2010 census===
As of the [[2010 United States census]], there were 427 people, 110 households, and 110 families residing in the CDP.<ref>{{Cite web|title=HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES: 2010|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Acacia+Villas+CDP;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2010.S1101|access-date=2023-07-17|website=data.census.gov}}</ref>

